A simple and elegant frontend demo of a Shopify-inspired online store created with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Project Summary:
This project replicates the look and feel of a Shopify product listing page. It includes:
- Product cards
- Add to cart buttons (only UI)
- Clean and minimal design
- Pure frontend only, no backend

Technologies Used:
HTML5
CSS3 (Flexbox layout)
JavaScript

Features:
- Product grid layout
- Responsive card design
- Basic UI interaction
- Simple and organized code structure

This is useful for showing Shopify-style development skills during job or internship applications.
